        nextStepId: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r010_c03
    - rid: 9129764570494402780
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r010_c03
        label: "R10 C3 Kaitora: This is where we spend most of o\u2026"
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Kaitora
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        showSpeakerName: 1
        sfxId: 
        text: This is where we spend most of our time, learning new combat skills
          and refining our magic techniques.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: vnchapter_1_kaitora_choice_r011_c03
    - rid: 9129764570494402781
      type: {class: VNChoiceStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: vnchapter_1_kaitora_choice_r011_c03
        label: Choice R11 C3
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        options:
        - text: Ask about the faculty
          nextStepId: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r012_c04
          kind: 0
          premiumPrice: 0
          effects: []
        - text: Ask why he wanted to meet you here
          nextStepId: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r012_c05
          kind: 0
          premiumPrice: 0
          effects: []
    - rid: 9129764570494402782
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r018_c03
        label: "R18 C3 Narrator: Kaitora clears his throat as if \u2026"
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        showSpeakerName: 1
        sfxId: 
        text: Kaitora clears his throat as if making sure he's understood.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r019_c03
    - rid: 9129764570494402783
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r019_c03
        label: "R19 C3 Kaitora: By the way, you can call me Kait\u2026"
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Kaitora
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        showSpeakerName: 1
        sfxId: 
        text: By the way, you can call me Kaitora. I don't place much value on titles.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r020_c03
    - rid: 9129764570494402784
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r020_c03
        label: "R20 C3 Narrator: You nod at your mentor. Kaitora \u2026"
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        showSpeakerName: 1
        sfxId: 
        text: You nod at your mentor. Kaitora is very practical. If a title doesn't
          help you get closer to your goal, why bother with it?
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r021_c03
    - rid: 9129764570494402785
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r021_c03
        label: 'R21 C3 Kaitora: I''m glad that you''ve joined us.'
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Kaitora
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        showSpeakerName: 1
        sfxId: 
        text: I'm glad that you've joined us.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r022_c03
    - rid: 9129764570494402786
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r022_c03
        label: "R22 C3 Narrator: He pauses. Stoic as ever, Kaitor\u2026"
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        showSpeakerName: 1
        sfxId: 
        text: He pauses. Stoic as ever, Kaitora furrows his brow as he clearly doesn't
          like what he's about to say.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r023_c03
    - rid: 9129764570494402787
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r023_c03
        label: "R23 C3 Kaitora: However, I also have to make sur\u2026"
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Kaitora
        pose: 0
        emotion: 6
        showSpeakerName: 1
        sfxId: 
        text: However, I also have to make sure you understand what's happening in
          the world beyond Chronosoul and what it means for the sentinels.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r024_c03
    - rid: 9129764570494402788
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r024_c03
        label: "R24 C3 You: He must be talking about recent \u2026"
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: You
        pose: 0
        emotion: 7
        showSpeakerName: 1
        sfxId: 
        text: He must be talking about recent rumors of demons lurking in a small
          town near the academy.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: vnchapter_1_kaitora_choice_r025_c03
    - rid: 9129764570494402789
      type: {class: VNChoiceStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: vnchapter_1_kaitora_choice_r025_c03
        label: Choice R25 C3
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        options:
        - text: Ask about the rumors
          nextStepId: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r026_c04
          kind: 0
          premiumPrice: 0
          effects: []
        - text: Ask for reassurance
          nextStepId: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r026_c05
          kind: 0
          premiumPrice: 0
          effects: []
    - rid: 9129764570494402790
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r029_c03
        label: 'R29 C3 Narrator: Kaitora furrows his brow again.'
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        showSpeakerName: 1
        sfxId: 
        text: Kaitora furrows his brow again.
