        label: "R15 C4 Kensui: Needless to say, the sentinels a\u2026"
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Kensui
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        showSpeakerName: 1
        sfxId: 
        text: Needless to say, the sentinels are well respected by Chronosoul's academic
          community and beyond.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r018_c03
    - rid: 9129764570494403002
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r012_c05
        label: "R12 C5 You: Thank you, Teacher Kaitora. Is t\u2026"
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: You
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        showSpeakerName: 1
        sfxId: 
        text: Thank you, Teacher Kaitora. Is there a particular reason you wanted
          to meet me here?
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r013_c05
    - rid: 9129764570494403003
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: vnchapter_1_kaitora_line_r013_c05
        label: "R13 C5 Narrator: Kaitora looks thoughtful for a m\u2026"
